Package: envoyctl
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ca-certificates
Description: Generate and manage Envoy config from small fragments
 A small tool that compiles manageable YAML fragments into a full Envoy config,
 validates it using Envoy, and applies it safely.
